  "title": "Service / Assistant Engineer (Class 3) | Entry level/ 5 Days/ Island wide",
  "description": "<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li><p>$2500 - $3000 + Allowance</p></li><li><p>5 Days</p></li><li><p>Class 2/3</p></li><li><p>MNC with better career prospects (AWS & VB)</p></li><li><p>West/ Central/ East Region<br /></p><p></p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li><p>Perform routine inspections, maintenance, and repairs on mechanical systems.</p></li><li><p>Provide technical support for troubleshooting and resolving mechanical issues.</p></li><li><p>Installing, setting up, and testing new equipment or systems.</p></li><li><p>Conduct quality checks on mechanical components and systems.</p></li><li><p>Assist in preparing inspection reports.</p></li><li><p>Handle some aspects of sales quotations and order processing.</p></li><li><p>Assist technician with additional projects as needed.<br /></p><p></p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Entry level is welcome to apply. On job training will be provided.</p></li><li><p>Diploma in any Engineering or equivalent.<br /></p><p></p></li></ul><p><strong>To Apply, kindly click on the \"APPLY NOW\" button</strong></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><strong>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Gean Hock Leng (R25126891</strong>)</p><p><br />\n\n</p>",
